data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Pelzer, SC! This brand-new single-story gem boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering the perfect blend of modern living and comfort. The open floor plan welcomes you with a seamless flow from the spacious living area to the dining space and a well-appointed kitchen, complete with sleek countertops and modern appliances. Escape to the tranquility of the master bedroom, featuring an ensuite bathroom for your private retreat. Two additional bedrooms share a stylishly designed bathroom, ensuring convenience for all occupants. Natural light floods the home, enhancing the inviting atmosphere. Step outside to your fenced-in yard, providing a secure space for outdoor enjoyment, whether it's gardening, playtime, or relaxation. The long driveway adds convenience and ample parking space, while the corner lot location amplifies curb appeal and natural light.
